{"tid":1537403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「求反駁」屋企人睇今朝now新聞話示威者一度阻止15歲少年送院","createTime":"2019-09-04T02:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T03:29:11.000Z","uid":101985,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ab237703e5943bbcf322c820e1d6e1b696f92f4b","tid":1537403,"uid":101985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:10:23.000Z","msg":"一時間搵唔到段片反駁佢地，求教"},{"pid":"d982e1c40389c18d812ddb3ecf67a11d8819acfa","tid":1537403,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:10:44.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"022d64ac173c9acc2d520d5889ee813082124b96","tid":1537403,"uid":233664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:12:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361540\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361540&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3IeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=c179a8e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361540&h=3ed4630b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361540</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】太子昨晚再發生警民衝突，期間一名21歲青年在港鐵站被多名警員按在地上制服，他一度表現無力，呼吸急促。有在場人士質疑警員延誤讓他接受急救，最後他要用氧氣罩送院，證實頭和頸部受傷。<br />\n<br />\n周二晚上約十一時，在太子港鐵站，最少六名警員合力制服一名男子，把他按在地上並趕走附近市民。男子初時仍能大聲講出自己名字和電話號碼。<br />\n<br />\n他雙手被扣在背後，其後警員散開。該名男子表現無力，被警員拖向一旁。他在地上接受急救，期間呼吸急促。<br />\n<br />\n有在場人士不滿警員延誤讓他接受急救，又質疑若把他送院警方會向他施以暴力，一度與警方口角，數名軍裝警員被包圍，警方舉起胡椒噴霧警告。<br />\n<br />\n防暴警員到場增援，該名男子最後要用氧氣罩由擔架床送院。<br />\n<br />\n他的父母到醫院探望指兒子21歲，面和頭部受傷，不願意評論警方的手法。<br />\n<br />\n一批市民到醫院急症室守候，為傷者打氣。"},{"pid":"cc3cf7107c968854cd797a062b4bca48c7d2422c","tid":1537403,"uid":165750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:12:52.000Z","msg":"有兩名男子被送往廣華醫院<br />\n<br />\n一名為21男子<br />\n站內拘捕受傷<br />\n佢老豆話佢目前清醒，但頭、面部受傷<br />\n<br />\n一名為15少年<br />\nb出口斷頸男子<br />\n目前在神經外科 有意識但未完全清醒"},{"pid":"797a056fb07bfc0d22421b3ea16b19c5323f4548","tid":1537403,"uid":284304,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ab237703e5943bbcf322c820e1d6e1b696f92f4b","tid":1537403,"uid":101985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:10:23.000Z","msg":"一時間搵唔到段片反駁佢地，求教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"唔洗駁<br />\n佢地唔會fact check<br />\n你fact check完佢地都只係會質疑你個fact check<br />\n有無阻佢地自己想知根本大把方法求證"},{"pid":"dd07f13fcb83213deb35062f4ba953914d482e4a","tid":1537403,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:15:13.000Z","msg":"邊度有講"},{"pid":"0cb1566a1c2d700dd5fb22d32d9c84c8b3248365","tid":153740